Objectives

- Understand the fundamentals of SQL Injection.
- Analyze HTTP requests using Burp Suite.
- Observe how login requests are processed by a web application.
- Identify an authentication bypass caused by insecure SQL query construction.
- Learn secure coding practices to prevent SQL Injection vulnerabilities.

